---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-32 bg-sand border-t border-ink/10">
  <div class="wrap-wide pt-16 pb-10">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-10 mb-14">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mb-3">Claire Montague</div>
        <p class="text-slate text-[15px] leading-loose max-w-md">
          A small counselling practice in Naarm / Melbourne's inner north. In-person in Northcote and online across Victoria. Working with adults on the harder, quieter parts of being a person.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase text-sage tracking-[0.18em] mb-4">Practice</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[14px]">
          <li><a href={`${base}/about/`} class="text-slate hover:text-deepsage">About</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${base}/approach/`} class="text-slate hover:text-deepsage">Approach</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${base}/what-i-help-with/`} class="text-slate hover:text-deepsage">What I help with</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${base}/sessions-and-fees/`} class="text-slate hover:text-deepsage">Sessions &amp; fees</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${base}/journal/`} class="text-slate hover:text-deepsage">Journal</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${base}/contact/`} class="text-slate hover:text-deepsage">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase text-sage tracking-[0.18em] mb-4">Visit</h4>
        <address class="not-italic text-[14px] text-slate leading-loose">
          Upstairs, 248 High Street<br/>
          Northcote VIC 3070<br/>
          Tue–Fri 10–7 · Sat 9–1<br/>
          <a href="mailto:hello@clairemontague.com.au" class="text-deepsage hover:underline">hello@clairemontague.com.au</a>
        </address>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-soft p-6 md:p-8 mb-10">
      <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase text-plum tracking-[0.18em] mb-3">If you're in crisis</p>
      <p class="text-slate text-[15px] leading-loose">
        This practice is not an emergency service. If you're in immediate distress or worried about your safety, please call <strong class="text-ink">Lifeline 13 11 14</strong> (24/7), the <strong class="text-ink">Suicide Call Back Service 1300 659 467</strong>, or in a medical emergency dial <strong class="text-ink">000</strong>. You are not a bother.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rule-soft pt-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-3 text-[12px] text-slate">
      <span>© {year} Claire Montague Counselling · PACFA Reg. 28640</span>
      <span class="font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[11px] text-sage">
        On Wurundjeri Woi-wurrung Country · Sovereignty was never ceded
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
